            </p>

            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li>Display summary statistics and KPIs (Key Performance Indicators)</li>
                <li>Filter and sort data dynamically with LINQ queries</li>
